---

<MainLayout
  title="Senad | DevOps Portfolio"
  description="AWS-certified DevOps engineer portfolio focused on secure automation, delivery reliability, and measurable cloud outcomes."
>
  <section
    id="home"
    class="section-anchor section-block"
    aria-labelledby="home-title"
  >
    <p class="section-kicker">DevOps & Cloud Engineer</p>
    <h1
      id="home-title"
      class="hero-title max-w-3xl text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-5xl"
    >
      Building reliable cloud platforms with practical automation
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-lead mt-5 text-base text-[color:var(--text-300)] md:text-lg">
      AWS-certified DevOps engineer helping hiring teams and freelance clients
      ship faster with lower operational risk. I turn cloud complexity into
      secure, automated delivery systems with clear ownership and measurable
      outcomes.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-actions mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="#projects" class="button-primary focus-ring">View projects</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="button-secondary focus-ring">Contact</a>
    </div>

    <ul class="mt-8 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3" role="list">
      <li class="card-surface p-4">
        <p
          class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[color:var(--text-300)]"
        >
          Hiring teams
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[color:var(--text-100)]">
          End-to-end platform ownership across architecture, delivery, and day-2
          operations.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="card-surface p-4">
        <p
          class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[color:var(--text-300)]"
        >
          Freelance clients
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[color:var(--text-100)]">
          Production-ready AWS foundations with practical automation and clear,
          transparent delivery communication.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="card-surface p-4">
        <p
          class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[color:var(--text-300)]"
        >
          Shared outcome
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[color:var(--text-100)]">
          Faster releases, fewer operational surprises, and maintainable cloud
          systems.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section
    id="projects"
    class="section-anchor section-block"
    aria-labelledby="projects-title"
  >
    <h2 id="projects-title" class="text-2xl font-semibold md:text-3xl">
      Projects
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-[color:var(--text-300)]">
      Selected infrastructure work delivered through markdown-driven content.
    </p>

    <div class="project-filters mt-6" data-project-filters>
      <div class="project-filter-bar">
        <!-- Lane: always-visible segmented tabs -->
        <div class="project-lane-tabs" role="group" aria-label="Filter by lane">
          <label class="lane-tab" for="lane-filter-all">
            <input
              id="lane-filter-all"
              class="sr-only"
              type="radio"
              name="lane-filter"
              value="all"
              data-lane-option
              checked
            />
            <span>All</span>
          </label>
          <label class="lane-tab" for="lane-filter-professional">
            <input
              id="lane-filter-professional"
              class="sr-only"
              type="radio"
              name="lane-filter"
              value="professional"
              data-lane-option
            />
            <span>Professional</span>
          </label>
          <label class="lane-tab" for="lane-filter-personal">
            <input
              id="lane-filter-personal"
              class="sr-only"
              type="radio"
              name="lane-filter"
              value="personal"
              data-lane-option
            />
            <span>Personal</span>
          </label>
        </div>

        <!-- Stack: separate dropdown trigger -->
        <div class="project-stack-wrapper">
          <button
            type="button"
            class="project-stack-trigger focus-ring"
            data-filter-trigger
            aria-haspopup="true"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="projects-filter-menu"
          >
            <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <line x1="4" y1="6" x2="20" y2="6"/>
              <line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/>
              <line x1="11" y1="18" x2="13" y2="18"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Stack</span>
            <span class="project-stack-count" data-filter-summary-label hidden></span>
            <span class="project-filter-trigger-chevron" aria-hidden="true">▾</span>
          </button>

          <div
            id="projects-filter-menu"
            class="project-filter-menu"
            data-filter-menu
            role="region"
            aria-label="Filter by stack"
            hidden
          >
            <div class="project-filter-stack-header">
              <p class="project-filter-section-title">Stack</p>
              <button
                type="button"
                class="project-filter-clear focus-ring"
                data-stack-clear
              >
                Clear
              </button>
            </div>
            <p class="project-filter-helper-text">Select one or multiple.</p>

            <ul class="project-filter-stack-options" role="list">
              {
                stackOptions.map((stack) => {
                  const stackValue = toStackFilterValue(stack);
                  const stackOptionId = `stack-filter-${stackValue}`;

                  return (
                    <li>
                      <label class="project-filter-option" for={stackOptionId}>
                        <input
                          id={stackOptionId}
                          type="checkbox"
                          value={stackValue}
                          data-stack-option
                          data-stack-label={stack}
                        />
                        <span>{stack}</span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                  );
                })
              }
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

    <ul class="project-grid mt-8 grid gap-4" role="list" data-project-list>
      {
        projects.map((project) => (
          <li
            class="project-card card-surface p-5"
            data-project-item
            data-project-lane={project.data.lane}
            data-project-stacks={project.data.stack
              .map((item) => toStackFilterValue(item))
              .join('|')}
          >
            <div class="project-card-meta">
              <span class="pill-chip" data-lane={project.data.lane}>{laneLabel(project.data.lane)}</span>
              <span class="project-card-date">
                {dateRange(project.data.startDate, project.data.endDate)}
              </span>
            </div>

            <h3 class="project-card-title mt-4 text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[color:var(--text-100)]">
              {project.data.title}
            </h3>
            <p class="project-card-summary mt-3 text-sm text-[color:var(--text-300)]">
              {project.data.summary}
            </p>

            <ul
              class="project-card-stack mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2"
              role="list"
            >
              {project.data.stack.slice(0, 4).map((item) => (
                <li class="pill-chip">{item}</li>
              ))}
              {project.data.stack.length > 4 && (
                <li class="pill-chip pill-chip--subtle">
                  +{project.data.stack.length - 4} more
                </li>
              )}
            </ul>

            <details class="details-panel mt-4" data-project-details>
              <summary class="details-summary focus-ring">
                <span class="details-summary-main">
                  <span class="details-summary-chevron" aria-hidden="true">
                    ▸
                  </span>
                  <span class="details-summary-label">
                    Details
                  </span>
                </span>
              </summary>

              <div class="details-content">
                <dl class="project-story" role="list">
                  <div class="project-story-item">
                    <dt class="project-story-term">
                      <span
                        class="project-story-icon project-story-icon--problem"
                        aria-hidden="true"
                      />
                      Problem
                    </dt>
                    <dd class="project-story-text">
                      {project.narrative.problem}
                    </dd>
                  </div>
                  <div class="project-story-item">
                    <dt class="project-story-term">
                      <span
                        class="project-story-icon project-story-icon--approach"
                        aria-hidden="true"
                      />
                      Approach
                    </dt>
                    <dd class="project-story-text">
                      {project.narrative.approach}
                    </dd>
                  </div>
                  <div class="project-story-item">
                    <dt class="project-story-term">
                      <span
                        class="project-story-icon project-story-icon--result"
                        aria-hidden="true"
                      />
                      Result
                    </dt>
                    <dd class="project-story-text">
                      {project.narrative.result}
                    </dd>
                  </div>
                </dl>

                <p class="details-kicker text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[color:var(--text-300)]">
                  Full stack
                </p>
                <ul class="details-stack-list mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2" role="list">
                  {project.data.stack.map((item) => (
                    <li class="pill-chip">{item}</li>
                  ))}
                </ul>

                <p class="details-kicker text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[color:var(--text-300)]">
                  Impact
                </p>
                <ul
                  class="details-impact-list mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm text-[color:var(--text-300)]"
                  role="list"
                >
                  {project.data.impact.map((impactPoint) => (
                    <li>{impactPoint}</li>
                  ))}
                </ul>

                <div class="details-actions mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  {project.data.links.github && (
                    <a
                      href={project.data.links.github}
                      target="_blank"
                      rel="noopener noreferrer"
                      class="button-secondary focus-ring"
                      aria-label="View project source code"
                    >
                      View code
                    </a>
                  )}
                  {project.data.links.live && (
                    <a
                      href={project.data.links.live}
                      target="_blank"
                      rel="noopener noreferrer"
                      class="button-secondary focus-ring"
                      aria-label="Open live project"
                    >
                      Live project
                    </a>
                  )}
                  {project.data.links.caseStudy && (
                    <a
                      href={project.data.links.caseStudy}
                      target="_blank"
                      rel="noopener noreferrer"
                      class="button-secondary focus-ring"
                      aria-label="Open project case study"
                    >
                      Case study
                    </a>
                  )}
                </div>
              </div>
            </details>
          </li>
        ))
      }
    </ul>

    <p class="sr-only" aria-live="polite" data-filter-status></p>

    <p
      class="mt-5 text-sm text-[color:var(--text-300)]"
      data-project-empty
      hidden
    >
      No projects match this filter yet.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section
    id="experience"
    class="section-anchor section-block"
    aria-labelledby="experience-title"
  >
    <h2 id="experience-title" class="text-2xl font-semibold md:text-3xl">
      Experience
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-6 mt-3 max-w-3xl text-[color:var(--text-300)]">
      Experience includes full-time DevOps progression at Valcon, freelance AWS
      delivery through Upwork, and earlier operations leadership at INA Grupa.
    </p>

    <ol class="experience-timeline" role="list">
      {
        experienceTimeline.map((item) => (
          <li class="experience-entry">
            <div class="experience-header">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[color:var(--text-100)]">
                  {item.role}
                </h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[color:var(--text-300)]">
                  {item.company}
                </p>
              </div>

              <p class="experience-period">{item.period}</p>
            </div>

            <ul class="experience-highlights" role="list">
              {item.highlights.map((highlight) => (
                <li>{highlight}</li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </li>
        ))
      }
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section
    id="skills"
    class="section-anchor section-block"
    aria-labelledby="skills-title"
  >
    <h2 id="skills-title" class="text-2xl font-semibold md:text-3xl">Skills</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 max-w-3xl text-[color:var(--text-300)]">
      Production-focused tooling used across full-time and freelance cloud
      delivery projects.
    </p>

    <ul class="skills-ledger" role="list">
      {
        skillGroups.map((group) => (
          <li class="skills-ledger-row">
            <h3 class="skills-ledger-title">{group.title}</h3>
            <ul class="skills-ledger-tags" role="list">
              {group.items.map((item) => (
                <li class="pill-chip">{item}</li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </li>
        ))
      }
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section
    id="certifications"
    class="section-anchor section-block"
    aria-labelledby="certifications-title"
  >
    <h2 id="certifications-title" class="text-2xl font-semibold md:text-3xl">
      Certifications
    </h2>

    <div class="certifications-layout mt-6">
      <ul class="certification-list" role="list">
        {
          certifications.map((certification) => (
            <li class="certification-item">
              <h3 class="certification-title">{certification.title}</h3>
              <p class="certification-issuer">{certification.issuer}</p>

              <dl class="certification-meta">
                <div class="certification-meta-row">
                  <dt>Issued</dt>
                  <dd>{certification.issued}</dd>
                </div>
                <div class="certification-meta-row">
                  <dt>Credential ID</dt>
                  <dd>{certification.credentialId}</dd>
                </div>
              </dl>

              {certification.credentialUrl && (
                <a
                  href={certification.credentialUrl}
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="certification-verify-link focus-ring"
                >
                  Verify credential
                </a>
              )}
            </li>
          ))
        }
      </ul>

      <aside class="tools-rail" aria-labelledby="tools-rail-title">
        <h3 id="tools-rail-title" class="tools-rail-title">
          Core tools used in delivery
        </h3>
        <ul class="tools-rail-list" role="list">
          {coreTools.map((tool) => <li class="pill-chip">{tool}</li>)}
        </ul>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section
    id="about"
    class="section-anchor section-block"
    aria-labelledby="about-title"
  >
    <h2 id="about-title" class="text-2xl font-semibold md:text-3xl">About</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 max-w-3xl text-[color:var(--text-300)]">
      I work in two delivery modes: embedded partner for hiring teams and
      focused consultant for freelance clients. In both cases, the goal is the
      same simple architecture first, reliable automation, strong security
      posture, and clear operational ownership after handover.
    </p>

    <ul class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3" role="list">
      <li class="card-surface p-4">
        <h3
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-cyan-300"
        >
          For hiring managers
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[color:var(--text-300)]">
          Dependable ownership from platform design to stable day-2 operations.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="card-surface p-4">
        <h3
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-cyan-300"
        >
          For engineering teams
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[color:var(--text-300)]">
          Practical CI/CD and infrastructure automation that removes bottlenecks
          without overengineering.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="card-surface p-4">
        <h3
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-cyan-300"
        >
          For freelance clients
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[color:var(--text-300)]">
          Security-first AWS delivery focused on measurable business outcomes
          and long-term maintainability.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
